--- !u!114 &1553324836
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1553324830}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2b3be5df36e2b704786896cd5ab1f02a, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NPC_FruitVendor
  CanInteract: 1
  MyLines:
  - Line: 'Good morning friend! What a lovely day! You look like you got going a
      little hastily this morning, can I offer you a smoothie?  '
    Terminator: 0
    Choises: []
  - Line: "I make them fresh every morning. There\u2019s all sorts of fruits and
      veggies from my farm in them. "
    Terminator: 0
    Choises: []
  - Line: "Those kids? Oh, I don\u2019t mind. Good to keep the youths fed, anyway.
      Plus\u2026 One of their mothers is the butcher across the street\u2026 swoon "
    Terminator: 0
    Choises:
    - Response: 'I would love a smoothie, thank you! '
      NextLineID: 3
    - Response: 'Do you have a crush on the butcher? '
      NextLineID: 7
  - Line: "Of course, let me just whip that up for you! Today\u2019s special is peach
      and mango\u2026 Oh, right. Today\u2019s special is just mango. Laugh. "
    Terminator: 0
    Choises: []
  - Line: "Hey, I know this is really cheeky but\u2026 could you do me a favour?
      I\u2019d love it if you could deliver one of these to the butcher. Mango is
      her favourite\u2026  "
    Terminator: 0
    Choises:
    - Response: Sure!
      NextLineID: 5
    - Response: "Sorry, I\u2019m busy!"
      NextLineID: 6
  - Line: "Thank you so much! Here\u2019s your smoothie, and here\u2019s the one
      for her. Oh, don\u2019t worry about payment, this one is on the house for doing
      me a favour! Have a wonderful day, my friend.  "
    Terminator: 1
    Choises: []
  - Line: "Oh, that\u2019s okay. Don\u2019t worry about it\u2026 I\u2019ll just\u2026
      go and deliver it myself\u2026 gulp. -to self- You can do this, you can do
      this! Oh, here\u2019s your smoothie. Wish me luck. "
    Terminator: 1
    Choises: []
  - Line: "Me? Oh! Hahaha, me? A crush on the butcher? That\u2019s\u2026 where did
      you hear that? I\u2019d never- that\u2019s so silly, haha! "
    Terminator: 0
    Choises:
    - Response: "I can tell her you\u2019re interested? "
      NextLineID: 8
    - Response: 'Your secret is safe with me. '
      NextLineID: 9
  - Line: "You\u2019d do that for me?? Oh my goodness, I\u2019d be so thankful. Here,
      take a smoothie on the house. I make them fresh every morning. Oh, oh! And
      take this one for her too. It\u2019s mango, her favourite. "
    Terminator: 1
    Choises: []
  - Line: "Sigh of relief Thank you so much. Take this smoothie on the house for
      your troubles. I think I\u2019d die of embarrassment. Enjoy! "
    Terminator: 1
    Choises: []
  - Line: "For me? Oh my goodness\u2026 I\u2019m blushing\u2026 I think I\u2019ll
      have to visit her after work today to say thank you! "
    Terminator: 1
    Choises: []
  ID: 13
